elhochdeutschen Originaltext von Gottfrieds Tristan-Fragment sowie in Band 2 eine moderne Übersetzung und eine umfassende Einführung in das Werk.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aKnecht, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKnecht, Peter.1 aMarold, Karl, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMarold, Karl, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchröder, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchröder, Werner.1 aTomasek, Tomas.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311089160740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110891607423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110891607/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014